data.enText: either of the pieces of skin above and below the eye that cover it when you blink or close the eye

data.chText: 不动声色；面不改色；眼睛都不眨一下
data.enText: to show no surprise or embarrassment when sth unusual happens

data.chText: 我把我最近的事告诉她时，她一点也不为所动。
data.enText: She didn't bat an eyelid when I told her my news.

tr: either of two folds of skin that can be moved to cover or open the eye
example: his lids would stay open no longer

value.def: Your eyelids are the two pieces of skin which cover your eyes when they are closed.
value.tran: 眼睑；眼皮 not bat an eyelid
